  "description": "Kyverno policy violations — counts, rate, top namespaces, webhook latency, recent PolicyReport entries. Metric names verified against Kyverno docs at install (chart 3.8.1 / appVersion v1.18.1); double-check after a chart bump as some names changed historically (kyverno_policy_rule_info → kyverno_policy_rule_info_total).",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 0,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "panels": [
    {
